ndgas industry flying searchandrescue and emergency medical missions and delivering maintenancerepairoverhaul and support services our capabilities are based on unique knowledge and accomplishment amassed from traveling out to and back from the worlds most remote and challenging destinations view restructuring information here chc ceo karl fessenden  back to basics prioritizing safety in a challenging economyin keynote remarks at the th annual chc safety  quality summit an internationally recognized aviationsafety event chc president and chief executive officer karl fessenden discussed the importance of ensuring that safety continues to remain a top industry priority  chc news chc helicopter celebrates  years of serving customers around the world jan    chc group today announced the beginning of a yearlong celebration of the operator’s year history since its humble beginnings as a crop dusting operation in british columbia in april of  vincent d’rozario joins chc helicopter as regional director asia pacific jan    chc group announced that vincent d’rozario has joined the company as regional director asia pacific chc australia reaches  hour milestone on aw jan    chc group announced it had recently reached the  flight hour milestone on its fleet of aws in australia more news careers join the thousands of experienced and talented people around the globe who work at chc search careers  safety  quality summit register now chc helicopter is proud to supportthe ihst safety initiative unauthorized access bizapediacom  human validation companiespeopleproductsservicestrademarksaddressesphone book our system has detected a high number of page requests from your ip address please prove to us that you are a human to continue using our website please send me to the search subscription offer page after i successfully answer the word challenge bizapediapro searchperform unlimited searches via ouradvanced search form withbizapedia pro searchfind out more bizapediapro databuild cust